    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require providers to offer a dual fuel social tariff for disabled/low earners ",
        "additional_details": "We feel the cost of energy in the UK is too high and that the cost of food / petrol / council rates have all increased. To heat our homes & keep warm should be more accesible to low earners and is enforceable by the energy regulator as a tariff for energy providers in the UK. We think an affordable social tariff needs implementing now",
        "background": "Require all energy providers to offer a dual fuel social tariff for disabled or low income / benefits claimants.",
